  "title": "Super-8 film of a UFO in Tatuapé-SP, [1978]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/14/delivery-receipt-of-super-8-film-referring-to-the-occurrence-of-a-ufo-in-tatuape-sp-1978/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1Gb",
  "content": "<h4 style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"color:#99ccff;\">WATCH THE VIDEO BELOW: </span></h4>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><strong>Translation of the reported case and delivery receipt</strong>:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&#8220;Mr. V.B., a lawyer, resident at  [&#8230;] n. [&#8230;], Tatuapé-SP-SP, which delivered, upon receipt, a KODAK Super 8mm color film, with a projection duration of approximately 4 minutes, stating that it was filmed from the street in front of the aforementioned residence by his brother P.A.B., 53 years sales manager. The footage is, according to Mr. V., of a strange object that hovered in the sky, at 02:30 am on December 30, 1978, and there may be a possibility of being a UFO. The machine used was a SUPER 8mm, with a Zoom lens with a magnification capacity of 8 times. The assignment of the film was made for research and is a copy, since the original is in the possession of Mr. P.&#8221;</p>\n<p><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/t59y7H3ckD4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.196. “Termo de entrega e recebimento de filme em super-8 referente a ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado em Tatuapé, Estado de São Paulo, em dezembro de 1978</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
